Insider Activity


Individual




John Moore Fowler



Mr. John M. Fowler is Independent Non-Executive Director at INTL FCStone, Inc. He is on the Board of Directors at INTL FCStone, Inc.
Mr. Fowler was previously employed as Chief Financial Officer, Director & Executive VP by Moneygram Payment Systems, Inc., Executive Vice President by Travelers Group, Inc., Chairman-Compensation Committee by Air Transport International LLC, and General Counsel by US Department of Transportation. He also served on the board at National Railroad Passenger Corp.



