I have a Mary Moore who married Isaac Fowler, who was my 6th gr aunt. Her parents were Thomas Moore and Rosannah Fowler. My connection is via Mary's brother Ephraim Moore who married Elizabeth Lindsey. Would love to talk to you. I know that your posting is an old one, but just happen to find it- Mary Moore and my Ephraim did have a sister named Deborah who married Jesse Fowler and they did have a son named Isaac. Could  this be your Isaac. Don't have a wife for him. Strange it would be another Mary Moore as wife, but possible???Judiththejcoriginal@aol.com





















