So glad to hear from you.  I know very little about your Ephraim Moore except I have him married to Sarah (Sally) Fox about 1798 in Laurens Co. S. C.  I have two children for them.I do not have dates of death for either of them.The Isaac Fowler I am looking for married Mary Moore, born about 1775, married about 1794.  I have wondering if Mary's sister, Deborah Moore born 1767, who married Jesse Fowler, son of John Fowler of Laurens Co. S. C. was married to a brother of Mary's husband, Isaac?  I have not have much luck with the Fowler's.My line is thru Mary's brother, Jesse, born 10 August, 1781.  Would love to exchange information.Thanks,Caroline





















